This folder contains input files required for running a series of dynamo benchmarks and tests.
Boussinesq and Anelastic benchmarks are split into the named folders.
All files required to run these simulations are in the relevant folders, EXCEPT for state.cdf.in.
These are larger files, and can be found elsewhere - TBD!

To run the cases, put parameters.f90 into the ./program folder, and any .txt.in files into the
install directory alongside main.out.
You will also need to obtain the state.cdf.in files and put them in the install directory.

Example output .dat files are included to compare results.
